  [lohs ah-BWEH-lohs]

el tío / la tía
  uncle / aunt
  [ehl TEE-oh / lah TEE-ah]

el primo / la prima
  cousin (m/f)
  [ehl PREE-moh / lah PREE-mah]

el sobrino / la sobrina
  nephew / niece
  [ehl soh-BREE-noh / lah soh-BREE-nah]

